    <string name="faq_room_creation">房间建立</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_create">如何建立3D房间？</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_create_answer">点击主屏幕左上角的照片图标，然后拍摄或选择房间的照片。您将看到两个选项来创建您的3D房间。</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_take_photo">如何拍照来创建房间？</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_take_photo_answer">点击主屏幕上的相机图标直接拍照。您可以选择标准(1x)或广角(0.5x超广角)镜头。保持设备稳定并点击拍摄按钮。照片将用于创建您的3D房间。</string>
    <string name="faq_two_methods">What are the two room creation options?</string>
    <string name="faq_two_methods_answer">When you select a photo, you can choose between: 1) AI-Powered 3D Room - automatically creates a realistic 3D room using artificial intelligence, or 2) Manual Setup - lets you draw the room boundaries yourself for more control.</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_airoom">What is AI-Powered 3D Room?</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_airoom_answer">This option uses smart technology to automatically turn your photo into a 3D room you can walk through. Just pick a photo and the app does the rest - no drawing or adjusting needed. It works like magic!</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_manual_room">What is Manual Setup?</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_manual_room_answer">With Manual Setup, you draw the outline of your room\'s walls on the photo. This gives you more control over exactly how the 3D room looks. It\'s great when you want to fine-tune the room shape yourself.</string>
    <string name="faq_which_method_better">Which method should I choose?</string>
    <string name="faq_which_method_better_answer">Try AI-Powered first - it\'s faster and works great for most rooms. If the result doesn\'t look quite right, use Manual Setup to draw the walls exactly where you want them. You can always try both and see which one you prefer!</string>
    <string name="faq_best_photos">什么样的照片效果最好？</string>
    <string name="faq_best_photos_answer">为获得最佳效果，请在光线充足的环境下拍摄，并保持相机水平。尽量拍摄整个房间，包括地板、墙壁和天花板边緣。避免模糊或昏暗的照片。</string>
    <string name="faq_generation_failing">为什么我的房间产生失败？</string>
    <string name="faq_generation_failing_answer">如果照片太暗、模糊或没有显示足够的房间特征，房间产生可能会失败。请尝试在更好的光线下以更宽的角度拍摄新照片。</string>
    <string name="faq_how_many_rooms">我可以建立多少个房间？</string>
    <string name="faq_how_many_rooms_answer">你最多可以建立10个房间。删除舊房间以腾出空间。房间数量显示在主画面顶部。</string>
    <string name="faq_furniture_segmentation">家具分割</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_segmentation">什么是家具分割？</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_segmentation_answer">家具分割使用AI识别和分离照片中的家具，让你看到每件家具在3D房间中的效果。</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_segment">如何从照片中分割家具？</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_segment_answer">检视3D房间时，点擊家具图示存取分割功能。选择包含家具的照片，应用程式将自动侦测并撷取家具。</string>
    <string name="faq_not_detected">为什么我的家具没有被侦测到？</string>
    <string name="faq_not_detected_answer">家具侦测在清晰、光线充足且家具明显可见的照片中效果最佳。确保家具没有被部分遮挡或与背景融合。</string>
    <string name="faq_multiple_pieces">我可以分割多件家具嗎？</string>
    <string name="faq_multiple_pieces_answer">可以！AI可以在单张照片中侦测多件家具。每个侦测到的物品将单獨显示，供你选择使用。</string>
    <string name="faq_room_fitment">3D房间与布置</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_view">如何检视我的3D房间？</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_view_answer">点擊主画面上的任何房间以开启3D检视器。你可以使用触控手势旋转、缩放和平移房间。</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_place">如何在房间中放置家具？</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_place_answer">分割家具后，点擊家具将其加入房间。然后你可以拖拽定位、捏合调整大小、旋转调整方向。</string>
    <string name="faq_sample_room">我可以使用范例房间嗎？</string>
    <string name="faq_sample_room_answer">可以！应用程式提供范例房间供你体验。从探索部分存取它們，无需先建立自己的房间即可尝试家具布置。</string>
    <string name="faq_accuracy">3D模型有多准确？</string>
    <string name="faq_accuracy_answer">3D模型能很好地近似你的房间布局。为获得最佳准确度，请确保原始照片清晰地捕捉房间尺寸，包括可见的角落和边緣。</string>
    <string name="faq_adjust_dimensions">我可以调整房间尺寸嗎？</string>
    <string name="faq_adjust_dimensions_answer">可以，进入设定并找到房间尺寸选項，你可以微调产生房间的大小和比例。</string>
